name: 17 CARAT
description_preview:
17 CARAT is SEVENTEEN’s first mini-album. It was released on May 29, 2015, with “Adore U” as its lead track.

The five tracks were all co-produced, co-written and performed by SEVENTEEN members. The group stated that the concept of this album was about “boy’s passion.”
